Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,基于 opentitles.org 英文字幕翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(注意：本字幕针对2020年动画版视频,\N与旧版本在对话内容和时间轴上略有差异)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\b1}The Faceless Ones: Episode 6{\b\b}\N{\b1\b1}无面一族: 第六集{\b\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,【中文翻译/时间轴】巴蛮子sz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在怎么办?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们溜出去, 看看能不能找到其他的年轻人. 快来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We slip away and see if we can find\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}all these young people. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, Blade 机长, 我们正在按你的指示\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, Captain Blade, we're following your instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找住宿中心呢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We're looking for the accommodation centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的指示对你们不适用\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My instructions don't apply to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩不再需要住的地方了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You two won't be needing living space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Blade 机长, 这是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Captain Blade, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂了, 我们是要留在这里的, 对吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't understand. We're here to stay, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 你们要留在这里, 不过不是以现在的形态\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yes, you're here to stay - but not in your present state.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很是抱歉, 但我还是没搞懂你的意思\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm very sorry, I simply don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟医疗中心核对过了, 你俩都是人类\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I checked with the Medical Centre. You're both human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们期望你们是完好无损的, 所以放你们过来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We want you intact. That's why I allowed\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你们的脑子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过了, 我不知道他们在哪里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've told you, I don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在我这里纯粹是浪费时间\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're wasting your time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他说的是实话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think he's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样, 带他出去!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid he is. Get him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们肯定在这里某个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They must be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方我们都搜遍了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We have completely searched this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在已经安排了50个人搜这一片\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've now got fifty men going through this part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦警察厅也正派人来帮忙\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and the Metropolitan Police are sending help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但时间已经不多了, 还必须搜遍整个机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But time is running short.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have to cover the entire airfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在需要志愿者!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I need volunteers now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接广播室\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get me the public address room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Heslington, 让所有入岗航班改道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Heslington, divert all in-bound aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,广播室, 这里是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Public Address Room, this is the Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把我切到广播系统\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Switch me through to the P.A. system
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,并且在收到下一步指示前, 暂停所有其它广播\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and stop all other announcements until further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是机场总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is the Airport Commandant speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家注意\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要所有机场人员协助执行一项特别任务\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want all available Airport personnel\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to assist in a special duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请各位到机场警局报告, 他们会给出具体指示\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Will they please report to the Airport Police,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who will issue instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,同时我也向各位乘客保证, 没有必要惊慌\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I would like to assure passengers\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that there's no cause for alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,并且很抱歉地通知大家, 所有出港航班暂停起飞\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and to apologise for the temporary suspension\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of all outward flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想在这里达到什么目的呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What did you hope to achieve here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求你给个机会, 为了五万年轻人的性命\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A chance to plead with you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for the lives of fifty thousand young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只不过是人类\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're only human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是宇宙中最智慧的种族\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We are the most intelligent race in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总管?   - 什么事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Director?  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,夫里堡的航班刚刚起飞了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Freiburg flight has just taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么, Jamie!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why, Jamie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想同我说话?   - 噢不想, 当然不想\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You wish to speak to me?  - Oh no, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你...你不是 Jamie, 你是个变色龙\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's... it's not Jamie. You're a Chameleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过, 我觉得你扮他扮得并不好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I don't think you've done a very good job on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么不好?   - 在转换过程中你丢掉了他的苏格兰口音\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Why not?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Well you lost his Scots accent in the processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是更喜欢原装的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh I much preferred the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 如果你是在找你朋友的原身, 在这里是找不到的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If you're looking for your friend's original,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, you won't find it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗?   - 找不到, 它在...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Really?  - No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...一个安全的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}...in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,离这里并不远. 我们还等什么呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Not far from here. What are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杜布罗夫尼克和雅典, 我们的人还在等着去接\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Dubrovnik and Athens.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're waiting to collect our personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比计划提前了好多, 可以等\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We're well ahead of schedule. We can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,继续, 开始转化\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Proceed with the processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对了, Blade 队长, 恭喜你把这个人带到这里来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}By the way, Captain Blade,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}congratulations on bringing this man here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我将亲自决断我们中谁将获得他的身份\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I personally will decide which of our people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}is to have his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是你的朋友中的某位, 毫无疑问\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It'll be one of your friends, I've no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是可以理解的...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,留在上面的这些特殊的人会有更多的安全感\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The special people up here feel more secure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们的原身就在卫星里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if their originals are actually in the satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴  - 总管没有什么需要担心的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Be quiet.  - The Director has nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的原身, Crossland 督察, 的确就在卫星上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}because his original, Detective Inspector\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Crossland is actually on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是, 你的原身在哪里呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But, where's your original?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And where's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,够了! 他们的原身都非常安全\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's enough! Their originals are perfectly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在盖特威克机场一个地方, 他们永远找不到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hidden on Gatwick Airport, where they will never be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我们的原身是什么意思?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What did you mean about our originals?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 据我的观察, 你们分两类\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, as I see it, there are two categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一类是跟你们总管和那边那个人一样...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}People like your Director and that man over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,....原身就在这里, 很安全\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}..whose originals are safe on board here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,另一类就是跟你们俩一样\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And then there are people like you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原身被留在盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}whose originals have been left behind at Gatwick airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果原身被搞坏了...你们就完蛋了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If they're tampered with... you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在撒谎\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快点, 赶在总管回来之前, 把他装进机器里去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on, let's get him into the machine\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}before the Director returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 你最好快点把我转化掉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, you'd better process me quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然你俩随时都会不存在了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}because any minute now you'll cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是名单上的第一个!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're first on the list!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么名单?   - 噢你肯定懂的!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What list?  - Oh surely you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经找到所有的原身了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've found all of the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,机场总指挥将会一个个把他们逆转换回去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Commandant at the Airport is going to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}deprocess them one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是第一个, 除非我阻止他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}starting with you, unless I stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在唬我们  - 等等!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He's bluffing.  - Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们在哪里找到原身的?   - 啊, 这我可不能告诉你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where did you find the originals?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Ah, that I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们已经搜了一段时间\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But they'd been searching for some time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而在我正要上飞机的时候, 我收到了信号\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and just as I was about to board the aircraft\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I got a signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就意味着他们已经成功了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}which meant that they'd been successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我也不会上来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Otherwise I wouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不信我, 找盖特威克机场核实一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, if you don't believe me, check with Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计你知道它的无线电频率吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I imagine you know its radio frequency?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,联系盖特威克机场塔台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Contact Gatwick Air Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经派了两打人赶过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got two dozen men moving down here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,搜索任何有被动过的痕迹的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}looking for any signs of the soil having been disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有二十个人, 还有五十个志愿者在排查这些机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There are twenty men here, with fifty volunteers\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}going through these hangars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总指挥  - 什么事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Commandant.  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在呼叫我们的频率\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Someone's crashing our frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁?   - 我不知道, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Who is it?  - I don't know sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个不明身份的电台, 要求同你通话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's an unidentified station, asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙总部呼叫盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Chameleon Headquarters calling Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听清吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是盖特威克机场总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Gatwick Airport, Commandant speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以清晰地听到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We are reading you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,据我们所知, 你们找到了一些我们感兴趣的东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We understand you have found some property\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in which we have an interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样吗?  - 是的, 我们有那个东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will you confirm? - Yes, we have that property.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说明你找到它的地点  - 这有关系吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- State where you found it.  - Does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是我们找到它了, 现在可以毁灭你们了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The important thing is we have found it,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and can now destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请在听筒旁等待\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please stay by your receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,博士肯定在跟他们使诈\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Doctor must be trying some sort of bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们却帮不上多少忙\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And we are not being much help to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你把它们放在哪里了?  - 不知道, 就在这里某个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where d'you think you left them?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't know, I left them in here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样, 不会是变色龙的人拿走了, 因为他们都已经走了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Anyway, none of that Chameleon lot could\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}have nicked them, 'cos they've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿, 看!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对了, 我突然想到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah. You see it suddenly dawned on me -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这里这么多车厢是在做什么呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}what would they be doing with so many coaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么没想到?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why didn't that occur to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 你一个人不可能有所有伦敦人的脑子啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, you haven't got all the brains in London you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,25个!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Twenty-five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看哈, 25辆车, 25个人!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There you are, twenty-five car numbers, twenty-five people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是变色龙总部\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Chameleon Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,解释一下你们为什么不愿意说明是在哪里找到那个东西的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Explain your reluctance to state\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}where you found the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不愿意的问题\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It is not a question of reluctance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就说警察还没告诉你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Say the police haven't told you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个东西在警察手中\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The property is in the hands of the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还没有告诉我之前是藏在哪里的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who have not yet informed me where the hiding place was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了, 请在听筒前等候\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Message understood. Please stay by your receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来接\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,航空控制塔台. 请等一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Air Traffic Control. Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个女孩和你的助理, 她们觉得找到了一个线索\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's the girl and your assistant.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They think they've got a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 我尽力拖住他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right, I'll try and stall them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,变色龙总部呼叫盖特威克机场, 我们现在开始返回\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Chameleon Headquarters to Gatwick Airport.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We are closing down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场呼叫变色龙总部, 你们能收到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Airport to Chameleon Headquarters,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场呼叫变色龙总部, 你们能收到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Airport to Chameleon Headquarters,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 盖特威克机场呼叫变色龙总部...  - 关掉\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Gatwick Airport to Chameleon Headquarters...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪收起来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Put that gun away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他说他们已经找到了我们的原身  - 那他找到了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He said he'd found our originals.  - And had he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 他在虚张声势\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, he was bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,继续转化吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Proceed with the processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以后, 你只能听我的命令\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In future, take your orders only from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会大吃一惊的, 等会儿你们就有25个人灰飞烟灭!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're going to get a surprise\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}when twenty-five of your people disintegrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜啊, 你看不到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What a pity you won't be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,护士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看看...你想让我做点什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then, now... what is it you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坐下  - 告诉我...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Sit down.  - Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在我被转化的过程中, 如果你解体了, 会怎么样?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}what happens if ah, you disintegrate\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in the middle of my being processed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是, 会对我造成什么伤害不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I mean, will that do me any harm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说, 会不会卡在某个状态与另一个之间之类的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}being suspended between one thing and an other,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}so to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 天\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该盯着他的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You should have been watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,重新取一个设备\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Send for a new unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你避免不了你的命运, 只不过推迟了一点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You haven't averted your fate, only postponed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,终于来了, 博士....\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}At last. Now Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你能肯定现在很安全了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're quite sure it's safe now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都就绪了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is everything ready now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下, 长官\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just one moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总管, 盖特威克机场又在呼叫我们了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Director. Gatwick Control calling us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别理他们  - 他们宣称已经找到了原身了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Ignore them.  - They claim they have found the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还是在使诈, 我说了别理他们!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're bluffing again, I said ignore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场呼叫变色龙总部, 你能听到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Airport to Chameleon Head Quarters. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还是没用, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's no good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那好, 我们得给他们个下马威\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Very well. We'll have to give them a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 警司\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right Super.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Erskine 警长吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sergeant Erskine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经找到了! 并不是在使诈\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They have found them! They weren't bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是他的设备出错了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}His equipment could have gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那好, 设备可能出什么错?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, what could have gone wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题得问我们的科学家\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That is a question for our scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等他们告诉你设备完全没问题的时候\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}By the time they tell you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that there's nothing wrong with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们全都解体了——当然除了这位总管\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}you'll all have disintegrated,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}except of course the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴, 这里没你什么事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Be quiet, this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 你完全正确, 这只跟他们俩有关\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, you're quite right, it only concerns these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我把嘴闭紧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll keep my mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好联系盖特威克机场台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'd better contact Gatwick Air Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们跟盖特威克机场没什么事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've finished with Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们跟我们还有事呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And what if they haven't finished with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是你自己的过失, 对不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That would be your own fault, wouldn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说所有的原身都藏好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You told me that all the originals were hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在一个不可能被找到的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where they could not possibly be found
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,直到有同胞失去生命了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until the life have been drained from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在才跟我说是你不小心?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you now telling me that you were careless?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,联系盖特威克机场塔台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Contact Gatwick Air Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,毁掉收发器\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Destroy the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是变色龙总部, 呼叫盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is Chameleon Head Quarters calling Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,盖特威克机场回复变色龙总部\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Gatwick Airport to Chameleon Head Quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能清晰地听到你的声音\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We are reading you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现在能说明在哪里找到的原身吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can you now state where you found the originals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是在汽车停车场发现的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The originals were discovered in a car park.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为了证明这一点, 我们已经消灭了你们的一员. 一个男人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}To prove it, we have already eliminated\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}one of your personnel. A man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我期望同博士说话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I now wish to speak to the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不能马上听到他的声音\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Unless I hear his voice immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个将被消灭的将是 Blade 机长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the next to be eliminated will be Captain Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放了他!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Release him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我说放了他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I said release him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到麦克风那里去!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get to that microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,先放了护士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Release the Nurse first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了我期望同博士说话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I said I wished to speak to the Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,否则下一个将会是 Blade 机长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}otherwise the next will be Captain Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 麦克风\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧, 亲爱的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you quite all right, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯, 我觉得没事  - 那就好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes, I think so.   - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 我是博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, this is the Doctor speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 真松了一口气\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ar, what a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等着, 我去谈判\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Stand by while I negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 我跟你们说说我的条件\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now then, I will tell you my terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以保障你们会继续存活\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I will guarantee your continued existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你们归还所有被绑架的年轻人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if you will return to Earth\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}all the young people you abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没用, 他们全都被缩小了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No use. They've all been miniaturised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那就逆转这个过程  - 恐怕那不可能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Then reverse the process.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'm afraid that's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 相应的设备在我们星球上  - 他在撒谎\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- The equipment for that is on our home planet.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那些飞机本身就是缩微操作室, 可以双向运作\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The planes themselves are the miniaturisation chambers\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and they work both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能以哪种形式继续存活, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What kind of continued existence would we have, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕只能是你们之前的形态\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In your former state, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的科学家得找出其它的方法, 来摆脱你们的困境\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Your scientists will have to find\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}some other way out of your dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,总比死了好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's better than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接受\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 我们接受\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, we accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是愚蠢, 怎么能相信他啊?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You fools, how can you trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小心! 啊...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look out! Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总指挥, 你还在那边吗?   - 在\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Commandant, are you still there?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谈判已按原定安排成功达成了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Negotiations have been successfully concluded as arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 那我就让停车场的人保持原样, 直到你们返回\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good. I'll leave the people in the car park as they are\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until you arrive back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 请继续监听这个频率\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good. Please stay listening out on this frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我将让 Blade 机长负责无线电\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am leaving Captain Blade in charge of the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你信得过他吗?   - 是的, 我想现在可以了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Can you trust him? - Yes, I think I can now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要尽力去找到我的三个朋友, 还有督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm going to try and find\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}my three friends and the Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道他们在哪里?   - 是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You know where they are?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你带我去找他们. 我会再同你们联系\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You will take me to them. I will call you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, Heslington, 赶紧过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, Heslington, flap over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽我们所能, 让一切快点恢复正常吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Let's get back to normal as quickly as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里, 我不知道具体是哪个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Over here. I don't know which one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 博士!   - Jamie! 哈!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Doctor!  - Jamie! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你还活着可真高兴\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm glad to see you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么...你什么意思?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How... how do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,回头再跟你说明吧, 现在赶紧出来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll explain to you one day. Well come along out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你站在那里就像个岗亭里的士兵\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You look like a soldier in a sentry box standing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事, 他是个朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's all right, he's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在坐下, 我找找其他人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now sit down while I find the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊! Crossland 督察, 你在这里啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah! Inspector Crossland. There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来, Ben, Polly, 回到盖特威克\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, Ben, Polly and back to Gatwick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 第一班飞机已经准备好起飞了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, the first plane is ready for take-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经让所有被转换的人上去了, 包括你的三个朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've got all the processed personnel\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}including your three young friends aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 很好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算跟我们一起吗, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you going with us, Doctor.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我打算跟 Pinto 护士一起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I'm going with Nurse Pinto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢, 督察?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you going Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 我最好在这里再待一会儿, 捋一下头绪\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, I think I'd better stay here just for a while,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to... tidy things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你准备好了吗护士?   - 是的, 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Are you ready nurse?   - Oh yes, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我陪你去飞机  - 咱们飞机上见, 护士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll see you to the plane.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll see you on the plane Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的未来会怎样, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What will our future be Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你们遵守你们的承诺\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}So long as you keep your side of the bargain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以毫发无伤地回到自己的星球\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}you may return to your own planet unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你们的科学家能找到一个方法, 来摆脱你们的困境\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Perhaps your scientists will be able to\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}find some way out of their dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也许能给他们贡献一两个点子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I may be able to give them one or two ideas of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 好, 我知道, 所有飞机跟你的飞机一样都在待命\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, yes, I know,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}all flights were suspended as well as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好博士, 都安全地下来了  - 是的, 是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Hello Doctor. All down safely.  - Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了, 太好了. 我现在得接这个布鲁塞尔的电话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Splendid, Splendid. I'll take that Brussels call now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就还有一件事, 总指挥  - 是, 是, 好的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- There's just one thing Commandant.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes, yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的TARDIS, 我们那个警察亭子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Our TARDIS. Our police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,(法语)啊, 布鲁塞尔. 是的, 我同意\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah Bruxelles. Oui, j'accord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跑道上那个警察亭子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The police box on the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当然, Jean, 帮博士取回他的东西, 行吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Of course, Jean, see that the Doctor\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}gets his property back, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再见博士, 非常感谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Goodbye Doctor and thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你总指挥  - 再见, 苏格兰小子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Thank you Commandant.   - Goodbye scottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再见, Samantha\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Goodbye Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快来Jamie, 我们必须找到Ben和Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come along Jamie, we must find Ben and Polly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还得找回 TARDIS\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and get to the TARDIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得道个别\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'd better say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 那回头见?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, well I'll see you around then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,回头在哪儿?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Around where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 你知道, 回头...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, you know, around...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊你不会就这样走了吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah you're not just going off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 我必须走. 否则博士...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, I must go. The Doctor'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦你弟弟马上就会到这里了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well your brother will be here any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那, 拜拜啦!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, ta-ra then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 感谢你所做的一切, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, thanks for everything, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说再见了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再见, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Goodbye Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行. 给总指挥带个感谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This will do. My thanks to the Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you every much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 博士, 你要去哪儿?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, Doctor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 回来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么? 我在找 TARDIS 啊, 当然了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doing? I'm looking for the TARDIS, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊, 我们就不能在伦敦待一小会儿吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh no, can't we stay in London a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊, 能回到正常可真是太好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah, it's good to feel normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正常? 你什么意思, Ben?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Normal? What do you mean, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是, 没有怪物, 没有赛博人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, no monsters, or Cybermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这些, 就很正常, 这是我的理解\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All this - it's normal. I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗, 变色龙观光游怎么说?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you? What about Chameleon Tours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 这是特殊情况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yeah, that was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我对于离开这里倒是很高兴\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh I'll be glad to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能把我们送到一个像1750年那样先进的地方吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can you not land us in a nice civilised place like 1750?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,1966年怎么就不先进了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's so uncivilised about 1966?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,得, 你自己留着吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, you can keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说这是1966年?  - 是\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Did you say 1966.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是几月?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What month is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,六月. 确切地说, 6月20号\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's July. July the 20th, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想到什么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你没明白吗, 小姐? 1966年6月20号, 一切开始的时间!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't you see, Duchess?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}July the 20th, 1966 is when it all began!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到了一开始的起点! 啊, 我觉得....\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We're back to when it all started! Well, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是说...就好像我们从来没有离开过!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That means it's as... it's as if we've never been away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真的想走, 是吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You really want to go, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个, 我们不会走的, 博士, 假如你真的需要我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, we won't leave, Doctor, if you really need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是, 这...这是我们的世界\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The thing is, it... it is our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们很幸运, 我就从来没能回到过我的世界...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're lucky, I never got back to mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧, 你们走吧!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, then. Off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,继续, Ben 可以赶上他的轮船, 成长为一位海军军官\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now go on, Ben can catch his ship and become an Admiral
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而你 Polly, 你可以照顾 Ben\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and you Polly, you can look after Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩注意安全, 好吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You will be safe, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会看着他的  - 我相信你会的, 老兄\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll look after him.  - I'm sure you will, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再见博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Goodbye Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能某个时候再见, 保重\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We might see you sometime. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得快点了, 总指挥的车在等呢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well you'd better hurry. The Commandant's car's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看他们走我有点伤感\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sad to see them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 Jamie, 我也是\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes Jamie, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过, 我们还有事情要做\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, we've got things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么事情?   - 哦, 我还没告诉他们, 不过...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What things?  - Well, I didn't tell the others but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的 TARDIS 丢了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've lost the TARDIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We can't have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才还在外面 - 但现在不在那里了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It was outside - it's not there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是说, 有人偷走了!   - 我不知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You mean somebody's stolen it?  - I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这正是我们要去搞明白的, 快点!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But that's what we're going to find out! Come on!
